<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="ride-n">ride <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /raɪd/    美 /raɪd/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>乘车；骑； (游乐园中) 供骑、乘的玩具：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Shall I <strong>give you a ride</strong> as you live so far away? 
你住那么远，我顺路捎你一程吧？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Although Dollywood has rides, the park’s main attraction is its culture. 
尽管多莱坞有骑乘游乐设施，但是这里最具吸引力的还是它的文化。</p><footer>人教④ – 5</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>rider /'raɪdə(r)/ n [C]<br />
riding /'raɪdɪŋ/ n [U]  </p></div>